abstract: Rory McIlroy makes his first competitive hole in one at Abu Dhabi Golf Championship, which Martin Kaymer leads going into third-round.
lead_paragraph: Simpson and Kuchar made enough birdies on the back nine to build a little separation and share the lead at the Sony Open in Honolulu.
